Package: E3ExpressionShiny
Title: Grant-Focused Shiny Reporter for the ARIA Plant E3 Resource
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Thorpe", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "p.thorpe@dundee.ac.uk")
    )
Description: A modular Shiny application for querying and visualising candidate
    discovery, OrthoFinder grouping, E3-domain, Expression Atlas, ligandability,
    pocket-conservation, three-dimensional alignment and provenance evidence.
    It reads a completed DuckDB, a single candidate-level master Parquet or all
    current-run Parquet results through lazy, bounded DuckDB and duckplyr
    queries.
